Make the GstAnalytics override optional.

Solaris does not deliver gst-plugins-bad, which provides the
gstreamer-analytics-1.0 dependency used by the new GstAnalytics override.

--- gst-python-1.28.2/gi/overrides/meson.build
+++ gst-python-1.28.2/gi/overrides/meson.build
@@ -1,4 +1,7 @@
